 - All values in input are integers.
 - 1 \leq N \leq 2000
 - 1 \leq M \leq 10^9

8

 - B = \{1, 2, 1\}, where \prod _{i = 1} ^N \dbinom{B_i}{A_i} = \dbinom{1}{1} \times \dbinom{2}{2} \times \dbinom{1}{1} = 1;
